snippet.textDisplay:
Roshe!!
This song is written by Habba khatoon the queen of Kashmir to her beloved husband Yousaf Shah Chak King of Kashmir State. Yousaf Shah Chak father Ali Shah Chak was from Hunza Gilgit present day( Gilgit Baltistan) before Yousaf his father was the ruler of Kashmir and when Mughal emperor Babur and Humayun attack Kashmir, Ali Shah Chak with his army defeated them 2 times and in the 3rd attempt Akbar finally invade Kashmir by betraying Yousaf Shah Chak and took him in prison in Bengal till his death...This song is in the memory of Sultan of Kashmir Yousaf Shah Chak.
